Summary: Passed over my house, very low, no sound, 4 blinking red lights in a kind of rectangle shape
divs: Sighting DetailsI was out on the back deck of our house smoking when I saw a set of 4 blinking red lights in a kind of rectangular shape pass over the house. They were moving from the west to the east, low and no sound was heard. The lights blinked intermittently but stayed in the same position in relation to each other. I went to the front of the house which faces north to see the object move away to the north-east. This is being entered on CMS by Steve Purcell as told to me by the witness.
